<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"> 
<title>菜鸟教程(runoob.com)</title>
<style> 
*{
	margin:0;padding:0;
}
#b
{
	width:100%;
	height:100px;
	overflow:hidden;
}
p
{
	width:449px;
	height:100%;
	border:1px solid black;
	float:left;
	background:red;
}
	#a{transition:all 3s;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<p><b>注意：</b>该实例无法在 Internet Explorer 9 及更早 IE 版本上工作。</p>

<div id="b">
	 <div id="a" style="width:2706px">
		   <p>www</p>
		   <p>www3</p>
		   <p>www4</p>
		   <p>www5</p>
		   <p>www6</p>
		   <p>www</p>
		   <span style="clear:both;display:block;height:0"></span>
	 </div>
</div>

<span>鼠标移动到 div 元素上，查看过渡效果。</span>
<script>
	var left = 0;
	var a = document.getElementById('a');
	setTimeout(function(){
	   left += 451;
	   
	   a.style.marginLeft = -(left) + 'px';
	    
	},5000)
	
	
	a.addEventListener('transitionend', function() {
		if(left>=2255){
			left = 0;
			 a.style.transition = 'none';
		     a.style.marginLeft = 0 + 'px';
			setTimeout(function(){
			   left += 451;
               a.style.transition = 'all 3s';
			   a.style.marginLeft = -(left) + 'px';

			},1000/60);
		}else{
		left += 451;
		a.style.marginLeft = -(left) + 'px';
		}
	},false);
	  
	
</script>
</body>
</html>


